highlights.text: “Miss The Rage (feat. Playboi Carti)” by Trippie Redd and Playboi Carti is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #19.
“Dick (feat. Doja Cat)” by StarBoi3 and Doja Cat is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 76 spots at #80.
Dua Lipa has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Levitating (feat. DaBaby)” is the highest at #4.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 223 weeks straight.
